name: Astro Globes: Orion Nebula
description:
Astro Globes is a series of uniquely processed astrophotography from my own collection with each image featuring a different object in our skies. 
The Orion Nebula or M42, is a diffuse nebula located in the constellation Orion. It is one of the brightest nebula in the night sky even visible to the naked eye. Dimensions 1924 x1660
